      "span_text": "Our findings are in accordance with those of previous reports that have revealed: (1) decreased levels of Map2 and impaired dendrite branching in primary CGNs from Vav3, a GEF for Rac, KO mice; (2) impaired dendritogenesis but not axonogenesis in Rac1-KD primary Fig. 10."
